summary: adds seven new dungeons and caves to find around skyrim, they use skymomod creatures only
descriptionHtml:
I forgot I still had this

its from the first version of skymomod, I went through and added a bunch of new creatures from the latest versions of skyrim monster mod
there are no vanilla creatures in here, its a kinda a creature sampler mod

I dont plan to update this again and it would be really cool if somebody could take this over

there is a areas.txt file included that gives the location of all the new interior cells 

this does require skymomod
author: Dogtown1
